  "key_patterns": [
    "All concrete drivers implement VcsDriverInterface via abstract VcsDriver",
    "API-based drivers (GitHub, GitLab, Forgejo, GitBitbucket) hold a ?GitDriver for fallback when API unavailable/unauthorized",
    "VcsDriver constructor is final; subclasses override initialize() for VCS-specific setup",
    "getComposerInformation() in VcsDriver uses Cache (40-char hex SHA = cacheable); SvnDriver overrides to use @rev pattern",
    "All drivers implement static supports() for URL-based driver selection",
    "GitHubDriver enriches composer.json with funding info, issues URL, archived flag",
    "GitLabDriver enriches composer.json with source URL, issues URL, archived flag",
    "PerforceDriver overrides getContents() to throw BadMethodCallException (no HTTP)",
    "SvnDriver uses trunk/branches/tags directory structure; configurable via repoConfig"
  ],

